Rules and Information
TOKYO
AND MORE.
Introducing America West's
Free Flight Plan.
America West's new Free Flight Plan lets you earn
credit toward exciting free travel awards whenever
you enjoy our less fare, more care service.
You'll earn Free Flight Plan certificates that
are honored by both America West Airlines and our
program partner, Northwest Orient Airlines. That
means every time you fly America West, you get closer
to London. Or Honolulu. Or Hong Kong. Anywhere
America West or Northwest Orient flies.
In addition to free tickets, your credit miles add
up to free or discounted rental cars and hotel stays
at several participating companies.
It's easy to get started with America West's Free
Flight Plan. Just pick up a Free Flight Plan coupon
book and brochure at an America West ticket counter,
or from your Travel Agent. And start flying the
less fare, more care way... more often.
Less Fare, More Care."
America West Airlines
